-- Reliance Communications in Talks to Sell 26% Stake to Vivendi, Times Says
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-06-23T01:31:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/reliance-communications-in-talks-to-sell-26-stake-to-vivendi-times-says.html

          
          
             India’s Reliance Communications Ltd.
is in talks to sell a 26 percent stake to Paris-based Vivendi
SA, the Economic Times newspaper reported, citing an official it
didn’t identify.  
